      options: ["Panic disorder", "Pheochromocytoma — paroxysmal hypertension + anxiety + palpitations + diaphoresis is the classic presentation; check plasma free metanephrines; treating this as primary anxiety without ruling out pheochromocytoma could be life-threatening", "Generalized anxiety disorder", "Social phobia"],
      correct: 1,
